import { monsterAC, monsterHP, monsterSpeed, monsterStr, monsterDex, monsterCon, monsterInt, monsterWis, monsterCha, monsterLang,randomMonsterInfo } from '../randomMaster'; import Table from 'react-bootstrap/Table'; export default function MonsterStats() { const moreMonsterInfo = fetch("https://api.open5e.com/monsters/?challenge_rating=&armor_class=&type=&name="+randomMonsterInfo+"&document=&document__slug=" ).then(result => result.json()); console.log("hight this is bubba "+ moreMonsterInfo) return (
STR DEX CON INT WIS CHA
{monsterStr} {monsterDex} {monsterCon} {monsterInt} {monsterWis} {monsterCha}
  • Armor Class: {monsterAC}
  • Hit Points: {monsterHP}
  • Speed: {monsterSpeed}ft
  • Languages: {monsterLang}
); }
